text: "Going Nowhere" is a song by English singer Gabrielle. It was written by Gabrielle and George McFarlane and produced by Pete Cragie for her debut studio album Find Your Way (1993). Released as the album's second single, "Going Nowhere" reached number nine on the UK Singles Chart and number 18 in Ireland.
